Tyrael was amazed. For a single bot to manage what he could not do... 
impressive!

Tyrael: I am afraid I know nothing about this... visitor of yours. I 
will look at what I can do, then, if we need to do something, I will 
contact you.

He closed the line.

Tyrael: Your opinion, Darkangel?
